      "numberInSurah": 10,
      "arabic": "فَأَنتَ عَنْهُ تَلَهَّىٰ",
      "french": "tu ne t'en soucies pas."
    },
    {
      "number": 5769,
      "numberInSurah": 11,
      "arabic": "كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذْكِرَةٌۭ",
      "french": "N'agis plus ainsi! Vraiment ceci est un rappel -"
    },
    {
      "number": 5770,
      "numberInSurah": 12,
      "arabic": "فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ",
      "french": "quiconque veut, donc, s'en rappelle -"
